{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03158/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03158"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:31:58"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["exterior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking, crane, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman talk on a hillside by the sea, holding hands."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03158","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03158"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/1be8d959-aa58-4000-bc74-9be7523d0b22","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:56:48.100Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s mysterious words recall <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW9095045 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01014.html\"><u>what he says of his mother</u></a> during his date with Alma. Despite his appreciation for and work with materiality (in the form of fabric, buttons, and the like), he is a Romantic soul plagued by visions of ghosts and with a desire for gothic love.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:677.2815533980582,80.19417475728153,386.79611650485447,349.5145631067961"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/e769fbe6-1555-4062-b689-9a8c88636d74","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:57:06.000Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The heart shape created by Reynolds and Alma holding hands resembles a heart in a variation of <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW48056402 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/punc-10716.html\"><u>this shot</u></a> from <em>Punch-Drunk Love.</em>&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:804.6601941747573,471.6504854368932,570.0970873786408,368.1553398058253"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1/05990d0a-d119-41fe-b871-c1b1884e2ed8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:57:20.099Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This shot evokes Brontëan romance and darkness along the lines of <em>Wuthering Heights</em>. This is a far cry from PTA’s San Fernando Valley—a willingness to explore other spaces.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03158/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:76.11650485436894,112.81553398058253,434.95145631067953,270.2912621359223"}}}]}]}]}